main event: Witnesses observed a bright white light that traveled toward the NNW for just under 2 minutes in Iowa City.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at approximately 10:40 PM,The object was about 200 to 300 feet above the ground and moving at a very high speed,Silent with a glow around the entire craft,The observer suspected it was an unrecognized type of aircraft due to its speed, altitude, and lack of running lights,Five witnesses were present during the sighting.
sighted object: a bright white light moving in the sky
witness description: A retired farmer and former member of the United States Army, along with other individuals.
